# üìù Workflow: Task Summary (Universal Template)

> **Use this when ANY AI agent needs to summarize completed work for handoff**

---

## üéØ One-Line Summary

```
Update task.md ‚Üí Create checkpoint JSON ‚Üí Create session summary MD ‚Üí Update PROJECT_STATUS.md ‚Üí Done
